Name: Super Star Path
About the game: Classic color match puzzle meets space shoot'em up action! Hop into your spaceship, open a path through huge waves of aliens and other hazards, and face intense boss battles! Three difficulty modes. Randomized color puzzle stages. Intense shoot'em up boss fights. Unlock, buy and upgrade new ships. Unlockable Boss Rush mode. Colorful and polished pixel art graphics. Arcade-like FM synth soundtrack.
